data.description: This Hewitt's open plan offers luxury and space, with a kitchen overlooking the living room and dining area.  The primary suite has a large walk-in closet and private bathroom.  Included are the 9' ceilings throughout, a study, 42" kitchen cabinets, granite countertops, tile floors and covered porch and patio. The large backyard also showcases a beautiful country view and open night sky. This home includes the backbone for a Smart Home ready for you to immediately enjoy.
